---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="攻略文章 - GameFi 攻略站">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">📝 攻略文章</h1>
  
  <!-- 分类筛选 -->
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8 justify-center">
    <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-gamefi-accent text-gamefi-dark rounded-lg font-bold">全部</button>
    <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-gamefi-card border border-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:border-gamefi-accent transition">新手指南</button>
    <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-gamefi-card border border-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:border-gamefi-accent transition">游戏攻略</button>
    <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-gamefi-card border border-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:border-gamefi-accent transition">收益策略</button>
    <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-gamefi-card border border-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:border-gamefi-accent transition">行业资讯</button>
  </div>

  <!-- 文章列表 -->
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- 文章 1 -->
    <article class="bg-gamefi-card rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-gamefi-accent border border-transparent transition">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
        <div class="w-full md:w-48 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">GameFi 新手入门指南</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">从零开始了解 GameFi，包括钱包设置、游戏选择、收益策略等全方位指南。无论您是区块链新手还是资深玩家，都能在这里找到有用的信息。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>📅 2026-03-06</span>
              <span>👁️ 1.2k 阅读</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/blog/getting-started" class="text-gamefi-accent hover:underline font-bold">阅读全文 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 文章 2 (占位) -->
    <article class="bg-gamefi-card rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-gamefi-accent border border-transparent transition opacity-60">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
        <div class="w-full md:w-48 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600 to-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">如何选择优质 GameFi 项目</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">教你识别有潜力的链游项目，避开土狗和骗局。从团队背景、代币经济、游戏玩法等多个维度进行分析...</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>📅 即将发布</span>
              <span>⏳ 准备中</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gamefi-accent font-bold">敬请期待</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
